# ==============================================================================
# INTELICS VOICE AI AGENT — .dockerignore
# Lives at: app/.dockerignore (inside the Docker build context folder)
# ==============================================================================
# This file tells Docker what to EXCLUDE when copying files into the image.
# Works exactly like .gitignore but for the "COPY . ." instruction in Dockerfile.
#
# Why does this matter?
#   - Smaller image size (don't ship compiled bytecode into the image)
#   - Faster builds (Docker doesn't hash excluded files for cache comparison)
#   - Security (never accidentally copy .env into the image)
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python compiled bytecode
# Python creates these automatically when it imports modules.
# They are machine-specific caches — useless inside a container.
# Including them would add bloat and potentially cause import confusion.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .env file — CRITICAL SECURITY EXCLUSION
# The .env file contains real secrets: Gemini API key, Gmail password, DB password.
# It must NEVER be baked into the Docker image.
# If it were in the image, anyone who pulls the image would see your secrets.
# Secrets are injected at runtime via env_file in docker-compose.yml instead.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Test output folders
# test_tts.py creates test_output_voices/ with 20 WAV files.
# These are large audio files that have no place in the production image.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
tests/test_output_voices/
*.wav

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Common development artifacts
# Exclude IDE configs, OS files, and other dev-only clutter.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Git metadata
# The .git folder is only needed for version control — not inside the container.
# Excluding it keeps the image smaller.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.git/
.gitignore